    Extended track report.

    This is a variable-sized structure on the network, since most of the fields are optional. The extMask field contains bit flags to indicate which of the subsequent fields are present on the network.

    Furthermore, note that this structure is subject to change without notice, including the size of the sensorSpecificData[] array. Use the sensorDataBytes field to determine how many bytes are actually valid in the array.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackExtended structure from "SPxPackets.h".
